    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine. This unit boasts a recently serviced high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies that provide exceptional throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance includes documented subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior displays minor road patina, the suspension geometry remains sharp with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring a visceral and connected driving experience. A robust, driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
